- apps/web/vitest.config.ts

Change:
- GET /api/ava/threads/:id now requires thread.user_id === current user and thread.team_id === currentTeamId().
- POST /api/ava/threads/:id/messages uses the same team-context owner check before reading request body or inserting a message.
- null team context only matches thread.team_id IS NULL.

